{"tid":1066390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中環站列車相撞］尖沙咀站月台過海實況","createTime":"2019-03-18T01:11:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T01:32:49.000Z","uid":131991,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3aa487b902e7d5b9fd192e9ceab74cebe5976187","tid":1066390,"uid":131991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:11:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PhJA3WW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhJA3WW.png&h=5c5e088d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n月台比平時少一半人，列車比平時少人<br />\n第一班往金鐘列車就上到<br />\n停左兩三分鐘先開+隧道停左分零鐘<br />\n金鐘站轉港島綫第一班車上到，人流比平時少<br />\n<br />\n相反紅磡搭隧巴去灣仔至中環301/104大堂人龍長到過左紅館<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似乎係有人以為荃灣綫過唔到海停埋金鐘，湧晒去紅磡搭隧巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc840c00c89fd130f8c2c5957602a71c921397e","tid":1066390,"uid":22069,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:16:06.000Z","msg":"屌 寧願搭船都唔撚會排過海巴<br />\n係咪on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9265b55c8a802850f7704a87f2b539577cd0d982","tid":1066390,"uid":190064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:27:45.000Z","msg":"唔怪得之紅隧塞到PK"},{"pid":"9f7bbfaee849e628eb90ed25adcc479299163711","tid":1066390,"uid":116709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T01:32:49.000Z","msg":"搭咩都遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n地鐵慢, 西隧塞, 紅隧仲塞"}]}